==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sise
<hw>Sise</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Sice</er>.]</ety> <def>Six; the highest number on a die; the cast of
six in throwing dice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In the new casting of a die, when ace is on the top,
<qex>sise</qex> must needs be at the bottom.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sisel</ent>⟦br⟧
